Title: Vengeance, Part 5
Writer: Chris Ryan (based on the book by), Richard Zajdlic
Actors: Philip Winchester, Sullivan Stapleton, Rhona Mitra, Rhashan Stone
Plot: Section 20 races to intercept a former South African nuclear scientist, Peter Evans, from Matlock. At the airport, they run into a team of Mossad agents who want to kill Evans. Section 20 learns that Knox is behind loss of the triggers.
